  "body": "### Description\r\nWith a 5-validator-node QBFT chain, stop one of the validators, delete its DB, then restart with `SNAP_X` sync mode. The sync completes, but the node never starts mining.\r\n\r\nI spotted this while raising/fixing https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/issues/5856. That issue resolved an `NPE` with both `FAST` and `SNAP_X` sync but with the latter, the node never starts mining.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\nAfter a successful `SNAP_X` sync with other QBFT nodes, a validator should continue mining new blocks.\r\n\r\n",
